sequenceDiagram
    participant P as PullMessageService
    participant C as DefaultMQPushConsumerImpl
    participant W as PullAPIWrapper
    participant A as MQClientAPIImpl
    participant B as PullMessageProcessor
    participant S as DefaultMessageStore
    participant Q as ConsumeQueue
    participant L as CommitLog
    participant E as ConsumeMessageService

    P->>C: pullMessage(PullRequest)
    C->>W: pullKernelImpl()
    W->>A: pullMessage()
    A->>B: PULL_MESSAGE
    B->>S: getMessage(topic, queueId, offset)
    S->>Q: 根据逻辑 Offset 定位物理位置
    S->>L: 读取消息本体
    L-->>B: GetMessageResult
    B-->>W: PullResult
    W->>C: processPullResult()
    C->>C: ProcessQueue.putMessage()
    C->>E: submitConsumeRequest()
